title: The Spelling Super Bowl
description: Since the Super Bowl is this weekend, we decided to do a Minnesota/Wisconsin City Spelling Bee and if you spell the city wrong, you have to take a shot of something that would be at a Super Bowl party. I.E. ranch, queso, beer.  Who got stuck with the Fireball shot??
